04","tid":1673082,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:08:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=0080d754\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=94682b2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=6a36e458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"1f731d452f176906c00ba303dbc1d5ee520ba6e3","tid":1673082,"uid":326712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a3cc5fe1ff45a295be271b88372c4f547e2ed5b","tid":1673082,"uid":321339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2W3KwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2W3KwC.jpg&h=96040423&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"邊度傳出黎?<br />\n新聞唔見有"},{"pid":"bad3fdac5fc6f49b7d7fbc2e0cc32420147f66fc","tid":1673082,"uid":321339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f731d452f176906c00ba303dbc1d5ee520ba6e3","tid":1673082,"uid":326712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a3cc5fe1ff45a295be271b88372c4f547e2ed5b","tid":1673082,"uid":321339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2W3KwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2W3KwC.jpg&h=96040423&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"邊度傳出黎?<br />\n新聞唔見有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1388650361310954/permalink/1478198692356120/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1388650361310954%2Fpermalink%2F1478198692356120%2F&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNq%2Bg